@startuml SendMessage

actor User as "Users"
boundary "ConversationDetailPage" as View #lightblue
participant ":chatRoute" as Route #lightblue
control "authMiddleware" as Auth #Orange
control "chatController" as Controller #lightblue
participant ":chatService" as Service #lightblue
entity "messageModel" as MsgModel #lightblue
entity "conversationModel" as ConvModel #lightblue
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB #yellow
participant "Socket Server" as Socket #lightgreen

    User -> View: 1. Type message content
    activate User
    activate View

    User -> View: 2. Click send button (or Enter)

    View -> Route: 3. POST /api/v1/chat/message
    activate Route

    Route -> Auth: 4. authenticateUser(req, res, next)
    activate Auth
    
    ref over User, View, Route, Auth, Controller, Service, ConvModel, MsgModel, MongoDB : 5. Middleware verifies access token & user role

    Auth --> Route: 6. authentication success
    deactivate Auth

    Route -> Controller: 7. sendMessage(req, res)
    activate Controller

    Controller -> Service: 8. sendMessage(readerId, senderId, content)
    activate Service

    Service -> ConvModel: 9. getDetailsByUserId(readerId)
    activate ConvModel

    ConvModel -> MongoDB: 10. ExecuteQuery()
    activate MongoDB
    MongoDB --> ConvModel: 11. Return conversation or null
    deactivate MongoDB

    ConvModel --> Service: 12. Return conversation
    deactivate ConvModel

    opt Conversation not found
        Service -> ConvModel: 13. createNew(conversationData)
        activate ConvModel
        ConvModel -> MongoDB: 14. ExecuteQuery()
        activate MongoDB
        MongoDB --> ConvModel: 15. Return new conversation
        deactivate MongoDB
        ConvModel --> Service: 16. Return conversationId
        deactivate ConvModel
    end

    Service -> MsgModel: 17. createNew(messageData)
    activate MsgModel

    MsgModel -> MongoDB: 18. ExecuteQuery()
    activate MongoDB
    MongoDB --> MsgModel: 19. Return new message
    deactivate MongoDB

    MsgModel --> Service: 20. Return new message
    deactivate MsgModel

    Service -> ConvModel: 21. updateMessage(conversationId, messageId, readerId)
    activate ConvModel

    ConvModel -> MongoDB: 22. ExecuteQuery()
    activate MongoDB
    MongoDB --> ConvModel: 23. Return updated conversation
    deactivate MongoDB

    ConvModel --> Service: 24. Return updated conversation
    deactivate ConvModel

    Service --> Controller: 25. Return message result
    deactivate Service

    par Emit new message to other user
        Controller -> Socket: 25.1. emitNewMessage(messageData, receiverId)
        activate Socket
        Socket --> View: 25.1.1. Broadcast 'new_message' to other user
        deactivate Socket
    else Emit conversation update to admin
        Controller -> Service: 25.2. getAllConversation()
        activate Service
        Service -> ConvModel: 25.2.1. getAll()
        activate ConvModel
        ConvModel -> MongoDB: 25.2.2. ExecuteQuery()
        activate MongoDB
        MongoDB --> ConvModel: 25.2.3. Return all conversations
        deactivate MongoDB
        ConvModel --> Service: 25.2.4. Return conversations
        deactivate ConvModel
        Service --> Controller: 25.2.5. Return conversations
        deactivate Service
        
        Controller -> Socket: 25.2.6. emitConversationsUpdate(conversations)
        activate Socket
        Socket --> View: 25.2.7. Broadcast to admin
        deactivate Socket
    end

    View --> User: 26. Display new message in chat
    deactivate View
    deactivate User

@enduml
